# _Pizza_

#### _This a project is an HTML page code review exercise for the evening Intro class at Epicodus, March, 2018_

#### By _**Thomas Doherty**_

## Description

_This is an HTML page styled with CSS and Bootstrap, using jQuery functions, constructor and prototype functions. The task was to create a website for a pizza company where a user can choose one or more individual toppings and a size to order a pizza and see the final cost.

## Specifications

* _Three options for pizza size using a radio buttons._
* _Four options for ingredients using a radio buttons._
* _Gather first name using a form group._
* _Create a pizza object constructor with properties for toppings and size._
* _Create a prototype method for the cost of a pizza depending on the selections chosen._
* _Give results to user by returning a string._
* -Reset page option._

